snippet: Andy Murray made a slew of unforced errors and was knocked out of the quarterfinals of the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif., by Juan Martín del Potro.
abstract: Juan Martin del Potro beats Andy Murray in BNP Paribas Open tennis tournament quarterfinals.
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray made a slew of unforced errors and was knocked out of the quarterfinals of the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif., by Juan Martín del Potro.
